hly%20one%20real%20cent%20per%20Robux%2C%20though%20they%20can%20be%20had%20cheaper%20with%20package%20deals%20and%20other%20promotions.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20interview%20in%20a%20gaming%20newsletter%20with%20well-regarded%20Roblox%20developer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-how-to-make-money-6-figures-month%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJanzen%20%26quot%3BJandel%26quot%3B%20Madsen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BGrow%20a%20Garden%26quot%3B%20was%20initially%20created%20by%20the%20teen%20who%20built%20it%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20Then%20Madsen%20acquired%20part%20of%20the%20game%20to%20build%20it%20out%20with%20a%20team%20of%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20got%20even%20bigger%20when%20Do%20Big%20Studios%2C%20a%20Florida-based%20company%2C%20also%20partnered%20in%20the%20game.%20The%20exact%20workout%20of%20who%20owns%20what%20isn't%20clear.%20Madsen%20and%20Do%20Big%20Studios%20didn't%20respond%20to%20my%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22602%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20neeiding%20more%20robux%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841adf79b2a601d01b25e92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22543%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BGrow%20a%20Garden%26quot%3B%20on%20Roblox%20requires%20you%20to%20buy%20certain%20elements%20if%20you%20really%20want%20to%20get%20ahead.%20You%20use%20the%20platform's%20%26quot%3BRobux%26quot%3B%20to%20buy%20the%20game's%20%26quot%3BSchekles.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBI%20screenshot%2FRoblox%2F%26quot%3BGrow%20a%20Garden%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5448d03-89da-4b49-8656-e1c69d693ca9%5C%22%3EI%20played%20'Grow%20a%20Garden'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BGrow%20a%20Garden%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20free%20to%20play%2C%20you%20start%20by%20planting%20some%20simple%20seeds%20(carrot%2C%20strawberry)%2C%20which%20quickly%20grow%20into%20plants%20that%20you%20can%20sell.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20that%20money%2C%20which%20comes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20game's%20virtual%20currency%2C%20the%20Sheckle%2C%20you%20earn%20more%20to%20buy%20even%20more%20seeds%2C%20eggs%2C%20animals%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurious%2C%20I%20tried%20it.%20You%20start%20with%20just%20enough%20Sheckles%20to%20buy%20a%20few%20carrot%20seeds%2C%20which%20you%20can%20plant%20in%20your%20garden.%20Compared%20to%20my%20real-world%20failures%20in%20vegetable%20gardening%2C%20the%20carrots%20grew%20satisfyingly%20quickly%2C%20which%20I%20then%20harvested%20and%20took%20to%20sell%20at%20a%20farm%20stand%2C%20using%20my%20Sheckles%20to%20buy%20more%20seeds%20for%20strawberries%20and%20more%20carrots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20strolled%20around%20the%20world%20beyond%20my%20own%20garden%20to%20look%20at%20the%20gardens%20of%20other%20players%2C%20who%20were%20milling%20about%2C%20buying%20seeds%20and%20selling%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20players%20had%20really%20elaborate%20setups%2C%20which%20must've%20taken%20days%20or%20weeks%20of%20play%20to%20build%20up.%20After%20not%20too%20long%2C%20I%20had%20about%20400%20Sheckles.%20The%20leaderboard%20showed%20I%20was%20playing%20with%20someone%20who%20had%20968%20million%20Sheckles.%20I%20walked%20over%20to%20see%20her%20garden%2C%20which%20was%20full%20of%20lush%20plants%20and%20blocky%20animals%20walking%20around.%20Her%20profile%20showed%20she%20had%20created%20the%20account%20in%20early%20May%20%E2%80%94%20quite%20a%20feat%20(or%20a%20lot%20of%20real-world%20money).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20to%20%26quot%3Bsteal%26quot%3B%20another%20player's%20crops%20%E2%80%94%20but%20for%20that%20and%20other%20things%2C%20you%20have%20to%20use%20real%20Robux.%20In%20general%2C%20the%20gameplay%20is%20similar%20to%20other%20games%20%E2%80%94%20over%20time%2C%20you%20do%20a%20thing%20to%20trade%20in%20points%20for%20more%20things%2C%20which%20takes%20time%20and%20patience.%20And%20if%20you're%20willing%20to%20spend%20real%20money%2C%20you%20can%20get%20ahead%20much%20faster%20(this%20is%20not%20unlike%20the%20real%20world).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270673017-50f9-4bda-afc9-182a081fe9a6%5C%22%3ESo%20what%20makes%20'Grow%20a%20Garden'%20so%20compelling%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Watkins%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20popular%20Roblox%20gaming%20YouTube%20channel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40thinknoodles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThinkNoodles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20me%20the%20game's%20creators%20obviously%20knew%20what%20they%20were%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20developers%20have%20really%20optimized%20everything%20about%20the%20game%20to%20maximize%20its%20spread%20in%20the%20Roblox%20algorithm%2C%20and%20also%20have%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20what%20players%20value%20in%20Roblox%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20many%20games%20that%20use%20different%20hooks%20for%20players%2C%20but%20this%20game%20has%20incorporated%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20into%20a%20single%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20live%20events%20that%20he%20said%20are%20considered%20%26quot%3Bmust-attend%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20%26quot%3Brich%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20virtual%20world%20of%20%26quot%3BGrow%20a%20Garden%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bflex%20on%20others%20with%20cool%20mutations%26quot%3B%20in%20your%20virtual%20patch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a903093f-1077-4cd2-99d5-7458b1669a65%5C%22%3EHow%20did%20'Grow%20a%20Garden'%20get%20so%20big%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrow%20A%20Garden%26quot%3B%20is%20undeniably%20popular.%20Roblox%20spokesman%20Eric%20Porterfield%20said%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20games%20that%20most%20quickly%20racked%20up%201%20billion%20visits%20in%20Roblox's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20adults%20in%20video%20game%20forums%20on%20Reddit%2C%20X%2C%20and%20YouTube%20have%20criticized%20the%20game%20as%20being%20for%20%26quot%3Bdopamine-addled%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20it%20doesn't%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20brain%20power%20to%20play.%20(To%20be%20fair%2C%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20adults%20who%20also%20said%20they%20found%20the%20game%20soothing%20and%20fun.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20said%20that%20Do%20Big%20Studios'%20involvement%20led%20to%20a%20bigger%20focus%20on%20monetizing%20the%20game%20%E2%80%94%20in-app%20purchases%20to%20get%20ahead%20and%20the%20like%20%E2%80%94%20which%20they%20said%20had%20put%20a%20damper%20on%20the%20game's%20community.%20(Again%2C%20I%20couldn't%20get%20Do%20Big%20to%20respond%20to%20my%20questions%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20they%20have%20to%20say%20about%20this%20criticism.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrow%20A%20Garden%26quot%3B%20is%20still%20new%2C%20having%20launched%20in%20March%202025%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20momentum%20and%20popularity%20it%20has%20doesn't%20suggest%20it%20will%20fizzle%20out%20anytime%20soon.%20After%20playing%20a%20few%20minutes%20a%20day%20for%20a%20few%20days%20%E2%80%94%20without%20spending%20any%20of%20my%20own%20money%20on%20Robux%20or%20Sheckles%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20grown%20my%20garden%20to%20more%20than%20180%2C000%20Sheckles%20with%20tulips%2C%20watermelons%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20a%20rare%20bamboo%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHard%20to%20complain%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrow-a-garden-roblox-robux-why-most-popular-explained-how-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749213648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841dddb9d73a0031e8df67f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrow-a-garden-roblox-robux-why-most-popular-explained-how-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roblox's%20%26quot%3BGrow%20A%20Garden%26quot%3B%20game%20is%20breaking%20popularity%20records.%20A%2016-year-old%20reportedly%20created%20it