c887%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222501%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Southwest%20Airlines%20Boeing%20737.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Carter%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Southwest%20flight%20from%20Nashville%20to%20Phoenix%20diverted%20to%20Oklahoma.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20passenger%20is%20accused%20of%20kicking%20and%20spitting%20at%20cabin%20crew%20after%20trying%20to%20open%20an%20exit%20in%20midair.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJendaya%20Kashar%20Brennan%20was%20charged%20with%20interference%20with%20flight%20crew%20members%20and%20attendants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-flight-diverted-day-after-new-rules-for-portable-chargers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20passenger%20was%20indicted%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20accused%20of%20assaulting%20a%20flight%20attendant%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20led%20to%20the%20flight%20being%20diverted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJendaya%20Kashar%20Brennan%2C%2030%2C%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassenger-twice-tried-to-open-planes-emergency-exit-police-say-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etried%20to%20open%20the%20plane's%20emergency%20exit%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20midair%2C%20says%20an%20FBI%20special%20agent's%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20May%2022%20on%20Southwest%20Flight%203239%20from%20Nashville%20to%20Phoenix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20Flightradar24%20shows%20how%20the%20Boeing%20737%20diverted%20to%20Oklahoma%20City%2C%20around%20halfway%20through%20the%20typically%203-hour%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrew%20members%20told%20the%20FBI%20special%20agent%20that%20Brennan%20told%20the%20flight%20attendants%20she%20wanted%20to%20get%20off%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrennan%2C%20who%20was%20sitting%20in%20the%20last%20row%2C%20tried%20to%20use%20the%20rear%20exit%20door%2C%20while%20a%20flight%20attendant%20had%20to%20block%20her%2C%20per%20the%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20after%20Brennan%20continued%20screaming%20and%20ignoring%20the%20crew's%20requests%20to%20stop%20trying%20to%20exit%20the%20plane%2C%20two%20passengers%20were%20asked%20to%20help%20restrain%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20somebody%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-flier-opens-exit-mistook-for-bathroom-local-media-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopen%20a%20plane's%20exit%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20midair%20would%20be%20a%20frightening%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20actually%20open%20the%20door%20at%20altitude.%20The%20cabin's%20pressure%20is%20much%20higher%20than%20outside%2C%20producing%20huge%20forces%20that%20keep%20the%20doors%20sealed%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20says%20that%20flight%20attendants%20started%20to%20apply%20wrist%20restraints%20to%20Brennan%20while%20she%20kicked%20them%20in%20the%20legs%20and%20spat%20at%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20says%20that%20Brennan%20tried%20to%20pull%20one%20flight%20attendant%20by%20their%20lanyard%2C%20before%20the%20crew%20also%20applied%20leg%20restraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrennan%20continued%20to%20fight%20the%20flight%20crew%20and%20broke%20her%20wrist%20restraints%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20passengers%2C%20who%20were%20retired%20correctional%20officers%2C%20held%20down%20Brennan's%20hand%2C%20per%20the%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20captain%20said%20he%20decided%20to%20divert%20the%20plane%20to%20Oklahoma%20City%20to%20prevent%20the%20flight%20attendants%20or%20passengers%20from%20being%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrennan%20continued%20to%20actively%20scream%20and%20yell%20until%20the%20flight%20landed%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20local%20police%20carried%20her%20off%20the%20plane%2C%20the%20affidavit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrennan%20was%20charged%20with%20one%20count%20of%20interference%20with%20flight%20crew%20m