h%2C%20an%20event%20tested%20how%20to%20improve%20manufacturing%20and%20logistics%20processes%20for%20future%20conflicts.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Thiep%20Van%20Nguyen%20II%2C%20PSNS%20%26amp%3B%20IMF%20photographer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFLEETWERX%2C%20defense%20industry%20partners%2C%20and%20the%20US%20military%20are%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20sustain%20the%20Navy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20recent%20event%20explored%20how%20to%20build%20and%20get%20critical%20materials%20to%20warfighters%20quickly%20and%20cost-effectively.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20process%20involves%20augmented%20reality%2C%20autonomous%20platforms%2C%20and%20other%20future%20warfare%20technologies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20future%20war%2C%20the%20US%20military%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20rely%20on%20traditional%20supply%20chains.%20Instead%20of%20flying%20or%20sailing%20in%20replacement%20parts%2C%20it%20may%20be%20forced%20to%20build%20them%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20wherever%20its%20forces%20happen%20to%20be%20%E2%80%94%20on%20land%2C%20at%20sea%2C%20or%20on%20remote%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20FLEETWERX%2C%20a%20project%20rethinking%20how%20the%20US%20military%20sustains%20its%20forces.%20Backed%20by%20DEFENSEWERX%20and%20the%20Naval%20Postgraduate%20School%2C%20it's%20working%20with%20industry%20partners%20and%20the%20US%20military%20on%20new%20ways%20to%20test%20and%20build%20critical%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20being%20done%20incorporates%203D%20printing%20technologies%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20augmented%20reality%2C%20and%20other%20emerging%20tech%20into%20solving%20key%20problems%20and%20overcoming%20logistics%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20May%2C%20FLEETWERX%20and%20its%20partners%20conducted%20an%20event%20testing%20how%20field-ready%20machines%20that%20can%20make%20or%20fix%20parts%20anywhere%20perform%20under%20real-world%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20stainless%20steel%20printing%20process%2C%20for%20example.%20Stainless%20steel%20is%20a%20vital%20material%20for%20building%20and%20repairing%20vessels.%20Having%20it%20readily%20available%20is%20key%2C%20but%20the%20logistics%20are%20less%20than%20ideal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20type%20of%20technology%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etraditionally%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20argon%20gas%2C%20so%20you%20have%20these%20big%2C%20giant%20green%20bottles%20that%20you're%20trying%20to%20transport%20all%20over%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20FLEETWERX's%20Lt.%20Col.%20Michael%20Radigan%20with%20the%20Marine%20Corps%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20expensive%2C%20and%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20points%20where%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20that%20gas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20camouflage%20and%20goggles%20looks%20inside%20a%20white%20machine%20that's%20printing%20materials.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841c6169b2a601d01b262b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20manufacturing%20machines%20need%20to%20be%20as%20deployable%20and%20self-contained%20as%20possible.%3Cp%3EFLEETWERX%2FDavies%20Public%20Affairs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20solution%20was%20a%20mobile%20nitrogen%20generator%2C%20an%20isolated%20unit%20inside%20of%20a%2010-foot%20container%20that%20could%20power%20a%20steel%20printer.%20That%20removes%20the%20logistics%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20put%20it%20on%20a%20ship.%20I%20can%20put%20in%20on%20a%20forward%20island%2C%26quot%3B%20Radigan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20do%20all%20of%20those%20things%20and%20I've%20cut%20my%20logistics%20train%20down%20dramatically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFLEETWERX's%20process%20typically%20starts%20at%20the%20top%2C%20with%20a%20commander%20or%20leader%20coming%20with%20a%20problem%3A%20a%20specific%20part%20or%20material%20is%20needed%2C%20and%20there%20are%20challenges%20with%20how%20to%20build%20it%20or%20get%20it%20where%20it%20needs%20to%20go.%20Drawings%20and%20plans%20are%20quickly%20made%2C%20and%20then%20it's%203D-printed%20in%20plastic%20for%20what's%20called%20a%20form%2C%20fit%2C%20and%20function%20test%2C%20basically%20determining%20if%20the%20product%20is%20the%20right%20size%20and%20will%20do%20what%20it's%20supposed%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20the%20technology%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20process%20is%20streamlined%2C%20is%20just%20one%20aspect%20of%20the%20work%20being%20done.%20The%20real%20focus%20is%20on%20understanding%20how%20it%20performs%20in%20an%20actual%20conflict%20and%20gets%20where%20it%20needs%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227605%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20manufacturing%20machine%20is%20seen%2C%20with%20various%20buttons%2C%20parts%2C%20and%20screens.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841c747c19ab3675c10b969%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225432%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAutonomous%20platforms%20cut%20the%20cost%20and%20time%20of%20delivering%20materials%20to%20service%20members.%3Cp%3EFLEETWERX%2FDavies%20Public%20Affairs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aim%20is%20to%20deploy%20these%20manufacturing%20machines%20into%20the%20field%2C%20where%20they%20can%20produce%20parts%20on%20demand%20and%20deliver%20them%20using%20autonomous%20platforms%20like%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadigan%20said%20that%20the%20advantage%20of%20using%20uncrewed%20systems%20is%20that%20a%20crewed%20aircraft%20isn't%20wasting%20time%20and%20resources%20flying%20parts%20that%20could%20be%20carried%20by%20a%20drone.%20The%20Navy%20has%20been%20experimenting%20with%20this%20concept%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpterodynamics-ceo-shares-secret-to-transwing-vtol-aircraft-innovation-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlueWater%20Maritime%20Logistics%20UAS%3C%2Fa%3E%20program%20to%20reduce%20the%20logistics%20demand%20on%20crewed%20aircraft%20and%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadigan%20compared%20the%20idea%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-prime-air-delivery-drones-too-loud-texas-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Prime's%20Phoenix%20drone%20delivery%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20the%20scale%20and%20speed%20that%20we%20need%20to%20be%20focusing%20on%2C%20but%20in%20a%20defense-related%20application.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20last%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navy.mil%2FPress-Office%2FNews-Stories%2Fdisplay-news%2FArticle%2F3877697%2Fimpact-at-rimpac-nps-students-enhance-fleet-readiness-with-3d-printing-technolo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERim%20of%20the%20Pacific%20exercise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20students%20from%20the%20Navy%2C%20Marine%20Corps%2C%20Army%2C%20and%20FLEETWERX%20researched%20how%20additive%20manufacturing%20equipment%20like%203D%20printing%20worked%20at%20sea%20and%20on%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubmarine%20repair%2C%20and%20shipbuilding%20more%20generally%2C%20were%20important%20topics%20at%20the%20event.%20Those%20industrial%20bases%20have%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-shipbuilding-problems-could-be-navys-achilles-heel-china-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esignificant%20shrinkage%20in%20the%20decades%20since%20the%20Cold%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20goals%20of%20revitalizing%20them%20have%20become%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20military%20leaders%2C%20industry%20partners%2C%20and%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20The%20emphasis%20isn't%20just%20the%20shipyards%2C%20though%3B%20there's%20also%20the%20work%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20May%20testing%20event%2C%20FLEETWERX%2C%20teams%20from%20across%20the%20military%2C%20and%20five%20private%20sector%20companies%20we