C%20'Well%2C%20shoot%2C%20where%20do%20I%20begin%3F%20I've%20got%20the%20manual%20here%2C%20but%20how%20do%20I%20get%20started%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEquipped%20with%20something%20like%20augmented%20reality%20goggles%2C%20a%20person%20could%20receive%20clear%20instructions%20on%20what%20steps%20to%20take%2C%20buttons%20to%20press%2C%20and%20how%20to%20use%20the%20machine.%20Largely%2C%20digitization%20of%20these%20and%20other%20processes%20is%20useful%20for%20building%20quickly%20and%20with%20much%20greater%20precision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20camouflage%20and%20goggles%20controlling%20a%20large%20manufacturing%20machine%20in%20front%20of%20him.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841cac09d73a0031e8df360%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20AR%20capabilities%20help%20any%20service%20member%20quickly%20learn%20how%20to%20use%20a%20machine.%3Cp%3EFLEETWERX%2FDavies%20Public%20Affairs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20potential%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-china-missile-problem-getting-worse-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewartime%20environment%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20service%20member%20may%20need%20to%20do%20repairs%20on%20a%20ship%20and%20work%20with%20a%20machine%20they%20haven't%20touched%20before.%20That%20AR%20aspect%20helps%20lighten%20the%20load%2C%20Radigan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%20has%20recognized%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-industry-needs-strengthening-long-war-with-china-army-secretary-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eneeds%20to%20adapt%20how%20it%20builds%20and%20gets%20materials%20and%20parts%20to%20forward-deployed%20forces%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Part%20of%20that%20com