%2Fcoast-guard-boot-camp-military-basic-training-cape-may-new-jersey-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECoast%20Guard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20excited.%20I%20loved%20boot%20camp%20%E2%80%94%20the%20way%20the%20military%20bearing%20was%20squared%20away%2C%20standards%20were%20upheld%2C%20and%20professionalism%20and%20respect%20for%20one%20another%20was%20maintained%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20I%20arrived%20at%20my%20first%20posting%20on%20a%20small%20Coast%20Guard%20station%2C%20everything%20was%20drastically%20different.%20It%20was%20the%20little%20things%20I%20noticed%20at%20first%2C%20like%20how%20they%20used%20first%20names%2C%20not%20rank%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20people%20on%20board%20took%20zero%20pride%20in%20grooming%20and%20uniform%20standards.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-work-culture-job-advice-great-resignation-careers-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eculture%20was%20toxic%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20men%20would%20openly%20read%20pornographic%20magazines%20in%20common%20spaces%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20culminated%20in%202005%2C%20when%20I%20was%20violently%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20one%20of%20the%20men%20above%20me%20in%20the%20chain%20of%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20attack%2C%20he%20hit%20me%20so%20hard%20that%20he%20dislocated%20my%20jaw%20%E2%80%94%20an%20injury%20that%20still%20causes%20me%20pain%2020%20years%20later.%20Since%20then%2C%20I've%20dealt%20with%20immense%20pain%2C%20both%20physically%20and%20emotionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb7cc34b-5e6b-4f8a-b384-58f9cff5d8fc%5C%22%3EFinding%20out%20I%20was%20pregnant%20saved%20my%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20trauma%2C%20I%20found%20moments%20of%20joy.%20After%20leaving%20the%20boat%20station%20where%20I%20was%20attacked%2C%20I%20moved%20out%20of%20state%20to%20Michigan%2C%20where%20I%20met%20my%20husband%20in%20the%20Coast%20Guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3C