rying%20to%20force%20people%20back%20into%20malls%20and%20movie%20theaters.%20Nothing%20wrong%20with%20the%20movie%20theater%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20a%20different%20world%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouston%20said%20a%20return%20to%20the%20office%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20when%20you're%20doing%20the%20same%20work%20you%20could%20do%20virtually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unproductive%20if%20you%20just%20sort%20of%20try%20to%20photocopy%20what%20you're%20doing%20in%20the%20office%20onto%20Zoom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20this%E2%80%94we%20can%20be%20a%20lot%20less%20dumb%20than%20forcing%20people%20back%20into%20a%20car%20three%20days%20a%20week%20or%20whatever%2C%20to%20literally%20be%20back%20on%20the%20same%20Zoom%20meeting%20they%20would%20have%20been%20at%20home.%20There's%20a%20better%20way%20to%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20many%20of%20Dropbox's%20tech%20peers%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-requiring-return-to-office-rto-mandate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emandated%20a%20return%20to%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20form%2C%20the%20company%20remains%20optimistic%20that%20it%20can%20accomplish%20just%20as%20much%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDropbox%20announced%20in%202020%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdropbox-letting-all-employees-work-from-home-permanently-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadopting%20a%20%26quot%3Bvirtual%20first%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20work%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20remote%20work%20outside%20of%20the%20office%20would%20be%20employees'%20primary%20working%20arrangement.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20the%20company%20began%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-return-to-office-dropbox-ceo-90-10-rule-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E90%2F10%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20employees%20work%20rem