%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841e6db9b2a601d01b26849%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223156%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECasey%20Cohen%20is%20the%20CMO%20of%20The%20Estate%20Registry.%3Cp%3EThe%20Estate%20Registry%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECasey%20Cohen%20started%20talking%20to%20his%20daughter%20about%20his%20estate%20plan%20when%20she%20was%20in%20elementary%20school.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20and%20his%20wife%20wanted%20to%20normalize%20the%20conversation%20and%20ease%20any%20of%20their%20daughter's%20doubts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECohen%20suggests%20all%20parents%20speak%20to%20their%20kids%20about%20their%20estate%20plan%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Casey%20Cohen%2C%20the%2053-year-old%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Festate-registry.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Estate%20Registry%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Festate-registry.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Estate%20Registry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20lead%20efforts%20to%20streamline%20the%20management%20and%20protection%20of%20family%20wealth%20across%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20at%20the%20Hippodrome%20Casino%2C%20RedRock%20Casino%20Resort%20%26amp%3B%20Spa%2C%20and%20Phillips%20%26amp%3B%20Cohen%20Associates%2C%20Ltd.%20before%20becoming%20the%20COO%20of%20The%20Estate%20Registry%20in%202023.%20I've%20been%20the%20CMO%20since%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20this%20is%20my%20line%20of%20work%2C%20it's%20important%20for%20everyone%20to%20speak%20to%20their%20children%20about%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Festate-plan-designed-make-sure-wealth-build-lasts-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eestate%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246c2d9fc-e076-4ea0-bcd9-5d8fe9fb8f29%5C%22%3EWhile%20I'm%20not%20a%20legal%20estate%20planner%2C%20I'm%20a%20subject-matter%20expert%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20completed%20my%20estate%20planning%20documentation%20prior%20to%20joining%20the%20firm%20in%202020%2C%20which%20brought%20up%20emotions%20of%20responsibility%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20father.%20I%20realized%20I%20was%20doing%20one%20of%20the%20most%20selflessly%20loving%20things%20I%20could%20do%20for%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20first%20talked%20to%20our%20daughter%20about%20this%20when%20she%20was%20in%20elementary%20school.%20We%20decided%20to%20introduce%20estate%20planning%20to%20her%20so%20she%20would%20understand%20from%20an%20early%20age%20that%20planning%20for%20the%20future%20is%20responsible%20and%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20confused%20at%20first%20about%20why%20we%20were%20starting%20the%20conversation%20at%20the%20dinner%20table%2C%20but%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20knew%20that%20rather%20than%20making%20it%20a%20one-time%2C%20heavy%20discussion%2C%20we%20had%20to%20normalize%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22654fb226-d279-4b5e-8e52-6978b825738e%5C%22%3EWe%20tried%20to%20introduce%20estate%20planning%20in%20a%20way%20that%20wasn't%20morbid%20or%20scary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20to%20explain%20to%20her%20that%20this%20decision%20expanded%20on%20our%20love%20for%20her%20and%20our%20need%2C%20as%20parents%2C%20to%20protect%20her.%20We%20explained%20that%20this%20was%20our%20way%20of%20ensuring%20that%20she%20was%20taken%20care%20of%20no%20matter%20what.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20didn't%20fully%20grasp%20the%20complex%20topics%20of%20guardianship%20and%20total%20estate%20documentation%2C%20but%20as%20time%20passed%2C%20knowing%20we%20had%20a%20plan%20in%20place%20eased%20her%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20eye-opening%20moments%20was%20when%20we%20discussed%20who%20would%20be%20next%20in%20line%20to%20take%20care%20of%20her%20if%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20passed.%20She%20proceeded%20to%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20if%20something%20happens%20to%20that%20person%2C%20too%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20great%20question%20and%20it%20made%20us%20realize%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20establish%20a%20backup%20plan%20for%20our%20backup%20plan.%20This%20takeaway%20applies%20to%20any%20parent%20%E2%80%94%20don't%20stop%20at%20just%20%26quot%3Btelling%26quot%3B%20your%20child%20what%20will%20happen.%20If%20your%20child%20is%20having%20doubts%20or%20certain%20fears%20regarding%20estate%20planning%20and%20their%20future%2C%20ensure%20that%20you%20take%20actionable%20steps%20that%20provide%20peace%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20sometimes%20now%20even%20brings%20up%20questions%20at%20the%20dinner%20table%2C%20which%20shows%20us%20she%20has%20become%20more%20comfortable%20with%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2428f5c-2fa3-45f4-a799-db256a338434%5C%22%3ETake%20the%20time%20to%20truly%20understand%20your%20own%20estate%20plan%20so%20you%20can%20confidently%20talk%20to%20your%20kids%20about%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWell-structured%20estate%20plans%20include%20a%20will%2C%20trust%2C%20beneficiary%20designations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-wasnt-ready-to-be-the-mom-of-adults-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epower%20of%20attorney%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20healthcare%20directives%2C%20and%20if%20you%20have%20children%2C%20this%20also%20includes%20guardianship%20designations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParents%20must%20explain%20what's%20in%20the%20estate%20plan%20and%20why%20certain%20decisions%20were%20made%20so%20their%20child%20feels%20informed.%20This%20involves%20updating%20their%20estate%20plan%20every%20few%20years%20or%20whenever%20there's%20a%20major%20life%20event%20(e.g.%2C%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20birth%20of%20a%20child%2C%20major%20financial%20changes)%20and%20ensuring%20their%20finances%2C%20from%20mortgage%20payments%20to%20credit%20card%20debt%2C%20are%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20your%20kids%20aren't%20involved%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process%2C%20they%20should%20still%20understand%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20plan%20and%20what%20to%20expect%2C%20but%20I%20made%20sure%20my%20daughter%20had%20a%20say%20in%20potential%20guardianship%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20your%20child%20turns%2018%2C%20have%20another%20conversation%20as%20your%20parental%20rights%20to%20access%20information%2C%20such%20as%20financial%20and%20medical%20records%2C%20change%20significantly%20and%20legally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ba1561f-fe95-4858-ae1e-c251390a4e00%5C%22%3EParents%20often%20make%20the%20mistake%20of%20not%20informing%20their%20children%20where%20their%20plan%20is%20stored%20and%20what's%20included%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParents%20need%20to%20tell%20their%20children%20where%20their%20estate%20planning%20documents%20are%20stored.%20It's%20shocking%20how%20many%20people%20create%20a%20will%20or%20a%20trust%20but%20then%20don't%20communicate%20where%20to%20find%20them%20or%20how%20to%20get%20into%20their%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20family%2C%20it's%20documented%20not%20only%20in%20legal%20paperwork%20but%20also%20on%20an%20online%20digital%20estate%20management%20platform%20that%20securely%20stores%20our%20information.%20We%20use%20LegacyNow%2C%20an%20Estate%20Registry%20product%20that%20safely%20stores%20our%20account%20information%20for%20all%20our%20asset%20and%20liability%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22417c9503-aa18-47df-b243-701f10027a8a%5C%22%3EEveryone%20should%20know%20that%20estate%20planning%20isn't%20just%20for%20the%20wealthy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEstate%20planning%20is%20essential%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20protect%20their%20loved%20ones%20or%20has%20any%20wishes%20they%20want%20to%20be%20honored.%20Everyone%20has%20something%20to%20add%20to%20a%20plan%2C%20whether%20that%20be%20an%20old%20car%20they%20bought%20years%20ago%2C%20insurance%20plans%2C%20or%20mortgage%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20piece%20of%20advice%20is%20that%20expecting%20parents%20should%20make%20an%20estate%20plan%20before%20their%20child%20is%20born.%20Use%20the%20time%20during%20pregnancy%20to%20draft%20a%20basic%20will%2C%20set%20up%20a%20guardianship%20plan%2C%20and%20ensure%20life%20insurance%20and%20financial%20accounts%20have%20the%20correct%20beneficiary%20designations.%20The%20sooner%20this%20is%20in%20place%2C%20the%20more%20secure%20your%20child's%20future%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20created%20an%20estate%20plan%20for%20our%20daughter%20while%20still%20expecting%2C%20and%20this%20gave%20us%20peace%20of%20mind%20from%20knowing%20that%20we%20had%20a%20plan%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20our%20daughter%20from%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223bc52f73-bb31-4786-b3f9-a4fb33cc49f7%5C%22%3EUltimately%2C%20if%20you%20plan%20earlier%2C%20you%20will%20likely%20face%20fewer%20uncertainties%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20pitfalls%20of%20not%20having%20an%20estate%20plan%20is%20that%20your%20assets%20could%20end%20up%20in%20probate%20%E2%80%94%20a%20long%2C%20expensive%2C%20and%20often%20frustrating%20legal%20process.%20With%20tech%20and%20digital%20estate%20management%20platforms%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20the%20process%20is%20becoming%20more%20streamlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEstate%20planning%20is%20about%20peace%20of%20mind.%20It%20ensures%20that%20your%20loved%20ones%20are%20protected%2C%20that%20your%20wishes%20are%20carried%20out%2C%20and%20that%20difficult%20decisions%20are%20made%20before%20they%20become%20urgent%20and%20emotional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStart%20early%2C%20keep%20the%20conversation%20open%2C%20and%20update%20your%20plan%20regularly%20because%20having%20a%20plan%20in%20place%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20gifts%20you%20can%20leave%20behind%20for%20your%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-talk-children-estate-plan-cmo-estate-registry-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749200701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841e9d29d73a0031e8df8a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-talk-children-estate-plan-cmo-estate-registry-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Casey%20Cohen%2C%20the%20CMO%20of%20The%20Estate%20Registry%2C%20started%20talking%20to%20his%20daughter%20about%20his%20estate%20plan%20when%20she%20was%20still%20in%20elementary%20school.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Perri%20Ormont%20Blumberg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-talk-children-estate-plan-cmo-estate-registry-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CAkshaye%20Khanna%20fired%20me!%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vidya%20Balan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749199758000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121671265%2Cimgsize-38036.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshaye-khanna-fired-me-vidya-balan-recalls-an-awkward-first-meeting-after-rejecting-a-film-opposite-him-went-to-john-abraham-for-help%2Farticleshow%2F121671312.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F121671312.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVidya%20Balan%20recently%20shared%20a%20humorous%20incident%20from%20her%20early%20career%20at%20the%20Bollywood%20Hungama%20Style%20Icons%20Summit.%20She%20revealed%20turning%20down%20a%20film%20with%20Akshaye%20