9CHulladek%20started%20as%20a%20business%20plan%20I%20presented%20during%20a%20college%20fest%20at%20St.%20Xavier%E2%80%99s.%20I%20proposed%20a%20model%20for%20collecting%20and%20recycling%20electronic%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20it%20won%20me%20the%20competition%20and%20an%20internship%20at%20E-Parisaraa%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20e-waste%20recyclers.%20That%20experience%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20my%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENandan%20spent%20two%20years%20working%20with%20a%20waste%20management%20company%20in%20Bilbao%2C%20Spain%2C%20rotating%20through%20procurement%2C%20logistics%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20dismantling.%20That%20global%20exposure%20helped%20him%20build%20a%20solid%20foundation%20for%20Hulladek%20Recycling%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHulladek%20is%20a%20Hungarian%20word%20for%20%E2%80%98waste%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20universal%20nature%20of%20the%20problem%20we%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20solve.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20seen%20waste%20not%20as%20a%20burden%2C%20but%20as%20a%20resource.%20That%20mindset%2C%20alongside%20the%20growing%20urgency%20of%20climate%20action%20and%20sustainable%20industry%2C%20cemented%20my%20belief%20that%20waste%20management%20is%20the%20next%20big%20revolution%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nandan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20belief%20soon%20turned%20into%20a%20movement.%20Hulladek%20Recycling%20stepped%20in%20to%20tackle%20a%20gap%20that%E2%80%99s%20often%20overlooked%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20waste%20story%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3Ee-waste%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20our%20old%20phones%2C%20broken%20chargers%2C%20defunct%20laptops%2C%20and%20discarded%20appliances%20quietly%20pile%20up.%20While%20they%20may%20seem%20like%20junk%2C%20these%20electronics%20are%20actually%20a%20goldmine%2C%20quite%20literally.%20They%20contain%20valuable%20materials%20like%20copper%2C%20aluminum%2C%20silver%2C%20and%20even%20gold.%20But%20they%20also%20carry%20a%20hidden%20danger.%20Toxic%20substances%20like%20mercury%2C%20lead%2C%20and%20cadmium%20can%20leach%20into%20the%20soil%20and%20water%2C%20harming%20both%20people%20and%20the%20planet%20if%20not%20handled%20correctly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hulladek%20Recycling%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20addressing%20the%20overlooked%20issue%20of%20e-waste%20in%20India%2C%20which%20contains%20valuable%20yet%20hazardous%20materials.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443719%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHulladek%20Recycling%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20addressing%20the%20overlooked%20issue%20of%20e-waste%20in%20India%2C%20which%20contains%20valuable%20yet%20hazardous%20materials.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20while%20conversations%20around%20plastic%20and%20biodegradable%20waste%20are%20growing%20louder%2C%20e-waste%20barely%20makes%20a%20whisper.%20It%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20most%20dangerous%20pollutants%20of%20our%20time%2C%20and%20still%20one%20of%20the%20least%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20Hulladek%20comes%20in%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20as%20a%20recycling%20company%2C%20but%20as%20a%20changemaker.%20With%20a%20mission%20to%20spread%20awareness%2C%20build%20responsible%20collection%20systems%2C%20and%20recover%20resources%20without%20harming%20health%20or%20the%20environment%2C%20Hulladek%20is%20working%20to%20turn%20a%20crisis%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20They%E2%80%99re%20showing%20that%20what%20we%20throw%20away%20could%20actually%20be%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20cleaner%2C%20more%20sustainable%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20bins%20to%20businesses%3A%20revolutionising%20e-waste%20recycling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%20Recycling%20works%20on%20two%20fronts%20%E2%80%94%20directly%20with%20everyday%20households%2C%20and%20in%20partnership%20with%20large%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20B2C%20(Business-to-Consumer)%20model%20brings%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F435253%2Fe-waste-disposal-phones-cords-guide-ngo-cpcb%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ee-waste%20awareness%20%3C%2Fa%3Eright%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20doorsteps.%20Through%20regular%2C%20door-to-door%20collection%20drives%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20helping%20families%20understand%20what%20e-waste%20really%20is%2C%20why%20it%20matters%2C%20and%20how%20to%20dispose%20of%20it%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20their%20B2B%20(Business-to-Business)%20arm%20supports%20big%20names%20like%20Godrej%2C%20Coca-Cola%2C%20Mondelez%20International%2C%20and%20Tata%20Steel.%20Hulladek%20handles%20these%20companies%E2%80%99%20e-waste%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20everything%2C%20from%20data%20destruction%20to%20compliance%20with%20government%20norms%2C%20is%20done%20thoroughly%20and%20transparently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20work%20has%20become%20even%20more%20urgent%20with%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1881761%23%3A~%3Atext%3DProducers%2520of%2520notified%2520EEE%252C%2520have%2Cbeyond%2520the%2520maximum%2520prescribed%2520concentration.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20E-Waste%20(Management)%20Rules%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20now%20in%20place.%20These%20rules%20require%20all%20manufacturers%20of%20electronic%20products%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20what%20happens%20to%20their%20products%20after%20use%20%E2%80%94%20a%20principle%20known%20as%20Extended%20Producer%20Responsibility%20(EPR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20companies%20must%20ensure%20their%20e-waste%20is%20being%20collected%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20disposed%20of%20safely%2C%20not%20just%20tossed%20aside.%20The%20law%20also%20sets%20clear%20targets%3A%20by%202023-24%20and%202024-25%2C%2060%25%20of%20e-waste%20generated%20must%20be%20recycled.%20That%20figure%20rises%20to%2070%25%20in%20the%20following%20two%20years%20and%20hits%2080%25%20from%202027-28%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20both%20individuals%20and%20industries%20to%20meet%20these%20goals%2C%20not%20just%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20operates%20with%20a%20dual%20approach%2C%20holding%20collection%20drives%20for%20households%20and%20managing%20e-waste%20for%20major%20corporations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20operates%20with%20a%20dual%20approach%2C%20holding%20collection%20drives%20for%20households%20and%20managing%20e-waste%20for%20major%20corporations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20their%20operation%20model%2C%20Shreya%20Khandelia%2C%20the%20Executive%20Vice%20President%2C%20Recycler%20Relations%20of%20Hulladek%20Recycling%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20initial%20collection%20of%20e-waste%20from%20our%20dedicated%20centres%2C%20the%20materials%20are%20segregated%20and%20sent%20to%20authorised%20recyclers.%20Recycling%20involves%20dismantling%2C