nt%2C%20solar-powered%20health%20systems%20across%20Northeast%20India.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-84_11zon-1749043166.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-84_11zon-1749043166-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-84_11zon-1749043166-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-84_11zon-1749043166-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-84_11zon-1749043166-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444236%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHuda%20Jaffer%20leads%20SELCO%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20build%20resilient%2C%20solar-powered%20health%20systems%20across%20Northeast%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20further%2C%20Huda%20Jaffer%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20SELCO%20Foundation%2C%20writes%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fselcofoundation.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMizoramBook.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFollowing%20the%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20book%20documenting%20this%20collaboration%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOur%20DRE%20system%20batteries%20come%20with%20a%20warranty%20of%20five%20years%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%20(MNRE)%3B%20if%20maintained%20very%20well%2C%20they%20run%20for%20about%20eight%20to%20ten%20years.%20Panels%20also%20come%20with%20a%20similar%20warranty%2C%20but%20they%20typically%20last%20abou